Similar to Search in Rotated Sorted Array (LC 33) but has duplicates

Algorithm
while(left <= right)

    mid

    Found target?
        return true

    Are left, mid, right all equal?
        left++
        right--
        continue

    Left sorted?
        Target in left?
            Search left
        Else
            Search right

    Else
        Right sorted
        Target in right?
            Search right
        Else
            Search left

return false




Solution:
/**
